title: Bodybuilding - Cory Everson - 3 videos
description:
Here are the 2 video tapes Cory Everson did and, a full body workout tape.

This 6 time Ms. Olympia winner put out some fairly good stuff for articles and videos in the 80's and 90's.  I don't have much of her but, I've used the full body workout when I was recovering from a bunch of injuries and, it made it easier on me.  Not being able to do much or lift weights (I was restricted to extremely light weights for months), that video kept me from going stir crazy.

More stuff to come, please help seed.:)
